text:
Hey, Producer.
Are we done with work for today?

Yeah, the interview just now was the last thing.
Sorry, it's been hectic lately.
It's been a bit busy, but…

I get to wear cute clothes and eat delicious sweets…
I'm having a lot of fun~
Hearing that makes me happy too.
Your smile brings happiness to many people.

So, I'll keep finding jobs
that make you smile.

Mm~
I'm looking forward to it~!
